items.sentence: Tom probably isn't the shortest person in the room.
Tom probably isn't going to be doing that tomorrow.
Tom probably isn't going to do that this afternoon.
Tom is probably not the best student in this class.
Tom is probably not going to ask Mary to the dance.
Even if you apologize to Tom, he won't forgive you.
Tom was the one who told me that he had to do that.
Tom was the one who told me Mary needed to do that.
Tom was the only one who didn't have enough to eat.
Tom was with us the last time we came to Australia.
